  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.22,
    "endTime": 19.5,
    "text": "Don't worry, your Pokemon will be fighting fit in no time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.5,
    "endTime": 21.43,
    "text": "Move it people we're losing him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.43,
    "endTime": 23.59,
    "text": "I need 50 CCs of hyperposin stat!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.59,
    "endTime": 24.613,
    "text": "On it Dr. Chancy!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.58,
    "endTime": 27.994,
    "text": "Don't you die on me you firey (beep)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.96,
    "endTime": 40.1,
    "text": "Doctor, he's not responding!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.1,
    "endTime": 43.49,
    "text": "And his internal temperature is down to 550 degrees celsius!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.49,
    "endTime": 44.323,
    "text": "Damn it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.323,
    "endTime": 46.44,
    "text": "That's practically freezing for a Charmander."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.44,
    "endTime": 47.989999999999995,
    "text": "Prepare for operation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.99,
    "endTime": 48.84,
    "text": "I need to scrub up!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.84,
    "endTime": 50.783,
    "text": "I got you Dr. Chancy!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.301,
    "endTime": 54.134,
    "text": "Oh no!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.572,
    "endTime": 58.241,
    "text": "What the (beep)."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.34,
    "endTime": 68.173,
    "text": "Clear!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.0,
    "endTime": 71.533,
    "text": "Clear!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.788,
    "endTime": 76.14,
    "text": "(beep) You Arceus, you're not getting this one today!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.14,
    "endTime": 77.373,
    "text": "Clear damn it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.97,
    "endTime": 88.503,
    "text": "Time of death 3:28 pm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.2,
    "endTime": 91.75,
    "text": "I'm sorry Doc."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.75,
    "endTime": 93.42,
    "text": "I don't know what happened."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.42,
    "endTime": 95.19,
    "text": "Oh I know what happened."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.19,
    "endTime": 97.52,
    "text": "You just lost your (beep) job!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.52,
    "endTime": 98.81,
    "text": "Get out of my OR!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.81,
    "endTime": 99.791,
    "text": "Now!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.791,
    "endTime": 102.341,
    "text": "Someone hold me back, I'm gonna murder this (beep)!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.86,
    "endTime": 111.053,
    "text": "Should I inform the trainer, doctor?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.21,
    "endTime": 117.42999999999999,
    "text": "You mean tell that poor kid out there that his best friend in the whole world is gone forever?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.43,
    "endTime": 122.23,
    "text": "No, the truth of what happened stays here with us and us alone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.23,
    "endTime": 126.23,
    "text": "You see, as doctors, our job isn't just to heal Pokemon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.23,
    "endTime": 130.96,
    "text": "We're the last line of defense against the cold harsh truths of this world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.96,
    "endTime": 134.44,
    "text": "If people really knew what went on, it would break them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.44,
    "endTime": 138.14,
    "text": "But not us, it's our purpose to carry that burden."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.14,
    "endTime": 139.52999999999997,
    "text": "Ours alone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.53,
    "endTime": 141.576,
    "text": "So what are you going to do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.65,
    "endTime": 146.703,
    "text": "Whatever I have to."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.9,
    "endTime": 165.132,
    "text": "I'm sorry, I'm sorry!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.132,
    "endTime": 166.933,
    "text": "Shh, it's almost over."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.17,
    "endTime": 172.14999999999998,
    "text": "Here you are!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.15,
    "endTime": 173.203,
    "text": "Good as new!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.35,
    "endTime": 176.66299999999998,
    "text": "Wow, I don't believe it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.397,
    "endTime": 182.14999999999998,
    "text": "Whoa, he's an even higher level than when I brought him in!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.15,
    "endTime": 183.94,
    "text": "And he learned new moves."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.94,
    "endTime": 187.63,
    "text": "And he's, a she?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.63,
    "endTime": 191.283,
    "text": "Yup, that happens sometimes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.29,
    "endTime": 196.51999999999998,
    "text": "Thanks, Nurse Joy!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.52,
    "endTime": 199.638,
    "text": "Oh, don't thank me, thank Dr. Chancy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.638,
    "endTime": 201.227,
    "text": "Chancy, Chancy!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.003,
    "endTime": 216.50199999999998,
    "text": "(beep) Chancy."
  }
]